eu.amidst.dynamic.examples.inference

Class DynamicIS_Scalability

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.dynamic.examples.inference.DynamicIS_Scalability
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AmidstOptionsHandler

    public class DynamicIS_Scalability
extends Object
implements AmidstOptionsHandler
    This example shows the scalability with respect to the number of cores of the Factored Frontier algorithm with the Importance Sampling inference engine, as described in Deliverable 3.4 (Section 6). (Note that the different number of cores has to be set from the operating system and run this experiment at least once with each configuration) Created by ana@cs.aau.dk on 25/11/15.
